The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-06-2014 THURS...PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


       
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/6/14Thursday, March 06, 2014 10:58 AM



Glenn reacts to a reporter working for Russia today,
    who resigns from her position live on air citing the fact that
      she can no longer sit by and work for a company funded by the Russian government
         and their actions. 

 Also, not one Democrat can think of a single accomplishment by Hillary Clinton,
     worth mentioning during her time as Secretary of State. 

 Plus, the president's approval numbers are dropping like a stone according to new polls.
